<div class="sect2 sect" id="ad-integration-samba-share"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">访问 Samba 共享</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">Samba 另一个用途是集成到一个现存的 Windows 网络。 一旦成为活动目录域的一部分，Samba 就可以为活动目录(AD)用户提供文件和打印服务。</p>
<p class="para">加入AD域最简单的办法是用<span class="app application">Likewise-open</span>。详细文档请参见 <a href="http://www.beyondtrust.com/Technical-Support/Downloads/files/pbiso/Manuals/ubuntu-active-directory.html" class="ulink" title="http://www.beyondtrust.com/Technical-Support/Downloads/files/pbiso/Manuals/ubuntu-active-directory.html"> Likewise Open文档</a>。</p>
<p class="para">成为"活动目录"的一部分后，在终端提示符处输入以下命令：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo apt-get install samba smbfs smbclient</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">下一步，编辑 <span class="file filename">/etc/samba/smb.conf</span>，修改：</p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">   workgroup = EXAMPLE
   ...
   security = ads
   realm = EXAMPLE.COM
   ...
   idmap backend = lwopen
   idmap uid = 50-9999999999
   idmap gid = 50-9999999999
</pre></div>
<p class="para">重启<span class="app application">samba</span>为新的设置生效：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo restart smbd</span>
<span class="cmd command">sudo restart nmbd</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">现在你应该能够从 Windows 客户端访问任何<span class="app application">Samba</span>共享了。但是，一定要给 AD 用户或者组分配合适的共享目录。请参考<a class="xref" href="samba-fileprint-security.html" title="Securing File and Print Server">Securing File and Print Server</a>获得更多详细信息。</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="ad-integration-windows-share"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">访问 Windows 共享文件</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">Samba 已经是活动目录域的一部分，您可以任意访问 Windows 的共享：</p>
<div class="list itemizedlist"><ul class="list itemizedlist">
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">挂载 Windows 文件共享，在终端命令行中输入：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">mount.cifs //fs01.example.com/share mount_point</span>
</pre></div>

          <p class="para">也可访问非活动域的计算机，不过，需要提供用户名和密码。</p>

        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">在系统启动时挂载共享，需要在 <span class="file filename">/etc/fstab</span> 中添加相应项，例如：</p>

<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">//192.168.0.5/share /mnt/windows cifs auto,username=steve,password=secret,rw 0        0
</pre></div>

        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">从 Windows 服务器拷贝文件的另一种方法是使用 <span class="app application">smbclient</span> 程序。 列出 Windows 共享的文件：</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">smbclient //fs01.example.com/share -k -c "ls"</span>
</pre></div>

        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">从共享中拷贝文件，输入：</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">smbclient //fs01.example.com/share -k -c "get file.txt"</span>
</pre></div>

          <p class="para">这将拷贝 <span class="file filename">file.txt</span> 到当前目录。</p>

        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">同时，拷贝文件到共享：</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">smbclient //fs01.example.com/share -k -c "put /etc/hosts hosts"</span>
</pre></div>

          <p class="para">它会将<span class="file filename">/etc/hosts</span>复制到<span class="file filename">//fs01.example.com/share/hosts</span>.</p>

        </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">

          <p class="para">以上使用到的 <span class="em emphasis">-c</span> 选项允许您同时执行多个 <span class="app application">smbclient</span> 命令，这有利于使用脚本及少量的文件操作。 <span class="em emphasis">smb: \&gt;</span> 命令行类似于 FTP 命令行，您可以使用它进行普通的文件目录操作，要进入其命令行，只需执行：</p>

<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">smbclient //fs01.example.com/share -k</span>
</pre></div>

        </li>
</ul></div>
<div class="note" title="备注"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents">
        <p class="para">使用您的服务器IP，主机名，共享名，文件名，以及一个有访问共享权限的真实用户名和密码，替换所有<span class="em emphasis">fs01.example.com/share</span>，<span class="em emphasis">//192.168.0.5/share</span>，<span class="em emphasis">username=steve，password=secret</span> 和 <span class="em emphasis">file.txt</span> 的实例。</p>
      </div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
